  "instructions": [
    "Prepare the miso marinade by mixing together miso paste, brown sugar, soy sauce, ginger, and garlic in a small bowl.",
    "Add the marinade to the pan over medium heat and cook for 2 minutes.",
    "Add the smoked salmon to the pan and cook for 2 minutes on each side, or until it flakes easily with a fork.",
    "Meanwhile, peel and dice the yukon gold potatoes and pan-fry them in a separate pan until golden brown.",
    "Add the pan-fried potatoes to the teppan and mix with the smoked salmon and marinade.",
    "Add the cream and sesame oil to the pan and stir to combine.",
    "Season with salt and pepper to taste.",
    "Transfer the hash to a serving plate and garnish with chopped green onions.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
  ],
